N 740 - 764 |JE| |N|It's really important that you reach 764, and stop there! You won't get multiple skill point for crafting yellow recipes, and the neck turns yellow at 780. This way when you craft your last neck recipe in the next step, it will still be orange and you will jump from 779 to 784. Otherwise you would have to make 4 more necklaces just to get from 780 to 784. <br/><br/> You can purchase the rank 2 recipes from (npc:100500) then you will need to discover the rank 3 recipes from World quest<br/><b>(spell:195927) World Quest, Highmountain<br/><b>(spell:209610) World Quest, Suramar<br/><b>(spell:195926) Drops from any creature in the Broken Isles.<br/><b>(spell:195928) World Quest, Azsuna| |P|Jewelcrafting 764| |NPC|100500|

